Spears::

She looked at him and listened. "I was with the Trainer for a while? 
How long was I with them? And how is it that I came back, but he 
didn't?" She a million and one questions run through her mind.

"Does he know that I'm back with you? If not, I may hav a plan to get 
him back. I can go back to the trainers, and pretend to still be one 
of them. Then I can get close to Striker, possably deactivate him and 
haul him back here."

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Firearm::
>

>

>

spent 
> alot of time with the trainers, but it was probably all gone with 
the 
> chip.
> 
> "The Trainers took you and Striker, that's as far as we know. We 
were 
> able to get you back with the weapon Ramulus designed, but it had 
> absolutely no effect on Striker. He .. just kept on shooting."
